$json = array('' => '');

Iz kontrolera:

From controller:
//JSON action helper
$this->getHelper('Json')->sendJson($json);

//From view script (.phtml file)
//json view helper
echo $this->json($json);

//Layout is being disabled
//View script rendering is being disabled
//Content-Type header is being set to 'application/json'
//Convert $json php variable into JSON (json_encode)
//echo json encoded variable into response body



output buffering
interno se poziva funkcija ob_start();
a na captureEnd() se poziva ob_end();
